      "file_path": "aai-core/src/main/resources/dbedgerules/DbEdgeRules_v12.json",
      "patchset_number": 3,
      "line": 300,
      "message": "the relationship between hpa-capability and cloud-region is hence \"BelongsTo\". Otherwise I didn't see why we need this associatedWith relationship.",
