      "unresolved": false
    },
    {
      "id": "5a93c517_d1cfaf54",
      "file_path": "aai-core/src/main/resources/dbedgerules/DbEdgeRules_v12.json",
      "patchset_number": 3,
      "line": 289,
      "message": "This would create a new instance of each HPA capability within each flavor. MANY2MANY is not a valid multiplicity if contains-other-v is not NONE",
      "author": {
        "account_id": 33,
        "name": "James Forsyth",
        "display_name": null,
        "email": "jf2512@att.com",
        "username": "jimmydot"
      },
      "updated": "2018-03-05 16:05:32.000000000",
      "in_reply_to": "5a93c517_dac909ad",
      "unresolved": false
    },
    {
      "id": "5a93c517_510b9f8d",
      "file_path": "aai-core/src/main/resources/dbedgerules/DbEdgeRules_v12.json",
      "patchset_number": 3,
      "line": 300,
      "message": "This would not make sense because cloud-region is not the direct parent of hpa-capability",
      "author": {
        "account_id": 33,
        "name": "James Forsyth",
        "display_name": null,
        "email": "jf2512@att.com",
        "username": "jimmydot"
      },
      "updated": "2018-03-05 16:05:32.000000000",
      "in_reply_to": "5a93c517_5abdf900",
      "unresolved": false
    },
    {
      "id": "5a93c517_c4db6b7a",
      "file_path": "aai-core/src/main/resources/dbedgerules/DbEdgeRules_v12.json",
      "patchset_number": 3,
      "line": 289,
      "message": "One HPACapability is referred by only one flavor. If 2 flavors has same HPA Capability it will be 2 different objects even though it has same parameters. So the relationship is MANY2ONE",
      "author": {
        "account_id": 1361,
        "name": "Dileep Ranganathan",
        "display_name": null,
        "email": "dileep.ranganathan@intel.com",
        "username": "dileep.ranganathan"
      },
      "updated": "2018-03-05 19:21:08.000000000",
      "in_reply_to": "5a93c517_dac909ad",
      "unresolved": false
    },
    {
      "id": "5a93c517_84e1e32b",
      "file_path": "aai-core/src/main/resources/dbedgerules/DbEdgeRules_v12.json",
      "patchset_number": 3,
      "line": 300,
      "message": "If we can agree on the fact that some HPACapability has flavor as parent and some has cloud-region as parent. We can give the relationship as belongsTo(parent-child) for both flavor and cloud-region, given the condition that the relationship will be exclusive. Christina mentioned this is possible so both cases can be accessed as follows \n\n…/cloud-regions/cloud-region/{cloud-owner}/{cloud-region-id}/hpa-capabilities/hpa-capability/{….}\nVs\n…/cloud-regions/cloud-region/{cloud-owner}/{cloud-region-id}/flavors/flavor/{flavor-id}/hpa-capabilities/hpa-capability/{….}",
      "author": {
        "account_id": 1361,
        "name": "Dileep Ranganathan",
        "display_name": null,
        "email": "dileep.ranganathan@intel.com",
        "username": "dileep.ranganathan"
      },
      "updated": "2018-03-05 19:21:08.000000000",
      "in_reply_to": "5a93c517_5abdf900",
      "unresolved": false
    },
