      "patchset_number": 7,
      "line": 303,
      "message": "If hpa-capability is a 'child' of cloud-region, contains-other-v should be !{direction} just like the flavor rule. Did you still also want the AssociatedWith 'cousin' edge from the hpa-capabilty under flavor to the cloud-region? Or is that idea being dropped.",
